Into the Woods is a modern twist on the beloved Brothers Grimm fairy tales 
in a musical format that follows the classic tales of Cinderella, Little 
Red Riding Hood, Jack and the Beanstalk, and Rapunzel-all tied together
by an original story involving a baker and his wife, their wish to begin 
a family and their interaction with the witch who has put a curse on them.
